00:16:49.000 --> 00:16:52.715
And they can be a
bit too overpowering.

00:16:52.715 --> 00:16:57.740
So not toasting the
nuts is a nice trick

00:16:57.740 --> 00:16:59.890
to keeping your food fresh.

